# Shadowrun Returns Preprocessor

Python script that processes Chinese `.po` translation files for Shadowrun Returns.

## What It Does

- Reads `.po` files from `materials/translations/`
- Uses `pinyiniser` to segment Chinese text and generate pinyin
- Joins segments with zero-width spaces (U+200B) for the runtime mod to consume
- Applies replacement passes: punctuation fixes, template token fixes, markup tag fixes, proper name pinyin joining
- Outputs compiled `.mo` files

## Dependencies

- `polib` — .po/.mo file parsing
- `pinyiniser` — Chinese tokenization, pinyin generation, special token handling (external library)

## Running

From `shadowrun-returns/chinese_preprocessor/`: `python main.py`
